	   <tr><td colspan=2>The best place I have found to practice safe fall is the hill to the east of the bridge at SK/NK zone (SK side).  If you turn left off of the end of the bridge you will see it.  Facing the river, if you run directly off the top, you can get 8 falls per trip down to the edge of the water. This only takes a little while to get your skill maxed at any given level.<br><br>*Just a note, I can't remember if I did this with or without spirit of wolf. Check it for yourself and see before you get too crazy with it.<br><br>Lathlelas<br>40 Druid<br>Seralok<br>20th Monk of CT<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
