	   <tr><td colspan=2>First off iksar monks are not neutral! they are still viewed to be evil to the rest off the world. Iksars have pros and cons so lets begin. Pro: iksars have infravision, so they see pretty well at night. Pro: all iksars can regen three times as fast as all other races (except trolls, they regen faster too) Pro: iksars start off with bounus ac. Pro: iksar monks have better overall melee stats then humans do. Con: iksars are hated all over the world! (but isnt that bad in my oppinion, I'll tell you why a little later) Ok now onto humans. Pro: they are tolerated in all good cities. Con: they have no special vision, they are blind at night (so get a light source ASAP!) So i would go with an iksar but its up to you. Also put all your points into mend until it gets to 100,(it should be at 100 at 19 i think) then you might wana be puting your other skill points into feign death or bind wound. ...ACK!! i just realized all this typing was a waste hehe, just check out monkly-business.com it has ALL you need to know about Monk: races,abilities, monk equipment, atk ratios, tips, and more..lol *bonks himself*<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
